  "sections": {
    "gp_section_572024258536932576": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "448aadf3595014e090d092e8ae2a24e2f4b59e914893af92c12a5f587dac13a5_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>Some feel <strong>relief within the first few hours</strong>. Others wake up one morning and realize they’re not reaching for painkillers anymore. It’s subtle at first. Then it’s life-changing.</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Clinically-Inspired. Chiropractor-Approved.",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "You’re Not Alone - And You Don’t Have to Live With the Pain",
        "ggDsiJqOuaL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e38939a8-c436-4251-9335-b4a95a4db445.webp",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "You’re Not Alone - And You Don’t Have to Live With the Pain",
        "ggfr_HLXtvq_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2a9dcc36-4169-409e-a1ad-38d053d4269c.webp",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Belt was developed alongside spine health specialists to deliver real, measurable relief without relying on medications or invasive treatments. <strong>Trusted by professionals</strong> and backed by thousands of successful outcomes, it’s designed with the same biomechanical principles used in <strong>modern physical therapy and chiropractic care.&nbsp;</strong></p>",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p>Over 57,000 people have already made the <strong>switch to SmoothSpine™ Belt</strong>, and the stories speak for themselves. From parents chasing after their kids again to weekend hikers finally hitting the trail pain-free – it’s working.</p>",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Clinically-Inspired. Chiropractor-Approved."
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258536932576"
    },
    "gp_section_572024258536998112": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "14f5c7f13ca388ba5f2a44a2bdc372e5367bf223e5c9808ad91f6173568a08f8_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>No prescription or appointment needed. It’s designed for safe, everyday use and follows the same biomechanical principles used in modern physical therapy and chiropractic care.</p>",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Not at all. The SmoothSpine™ Belt is slim, breathable, and designed to fit under clothes. You’ll forget you’re even wearing it until you notice the pain’s gone.</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Yes if your pain is rooted in SI joint instability, sciatica, or lower back strain, the SmoothSpine™ Belt is designed for exactly that. Most users feel relief within the first few wears, and even deeper results after 1–2 weeks of consistent use.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Just 2 to 3 hours a day is enough to feel a difference. You can wear it while walking, working, doing chores. No need to sit still or build your day around it.</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Will this actually help with my pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>How long do I have to wear it each day?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>Is it bulky or uncomfortable to wear?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Do I need to see a doctor to use this?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>I’ve tried other back braces, why is this different?</p>",
        "ggrcqOh_tmz_text": "<p>Most braces try to fix everything with stiffness. SmoothSpine™ is different. It uses targeted compression and adaptive support to stabilize the source of your pain (the SI joint), rather than just locking your whole back in place.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258536998112"
    },
    "gp_section_572024258537063648": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "be7688950824bb3e79a0b5e6f5c8dc7223a7a9cbd3b386be7dc9230bd9786d6a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "How It Works (and Why It Actually Does)",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Belt supports your body where it needs it most - <strong>right at the base of your spine.</strong></p>",
        "ggLpXZltW4C_text": "<p>As you wear it, the belt promotes healthy blood flow, reduces inflammation, and <strong>supports your natural alignment</strong> so you're not just masking the pain, you're actually addressing the cause.</p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "How It Works (and Why It Actually Does)",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>It wraps around your hips and uses dual compression zones to stabilize your SI joint and lower back, which <strong>helps relieve pressure from the sciatic nerve</strong>. This means less pain, more mobility, and better posture, starting from day one.</p>",
        "ggrjLQVb1BS_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-26f7cb83-6717-4508-a535-ca1c07b9a48c.webp"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258537063648"
    },
    "gp_section_572024258537129184": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f23a828894588b32a70090cb6e834c73e53941a2d2721ac640ea1ab410840b9b_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2skFYSnGC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-51bd7b08-f4ec-461e-bc36-e7734dd26e06.jpg",
        "ggBZyLN-waC_text": "<p>Your order today is protected by our iron-clad 90-day <strong>100% money-back guarantee. </strong>If you don't experience the remarkable <strong>relief from Back pain and Sciatica</strong> that you were anticipating, or if you're not amazed by how much easier it is to move, then at any time in the next <strong>90 days,</strong> let us know and we will refund every single penny of your investment. <strong>No questions asked.</strong></p>",
        "ggY5Kp_-GFD_text": "100% SATISFACTION<br>90-DAY MONEY BACK GUARANTEE",
        "ggufORTUxtU_text": "<p>We have 24/7/365 Online Email Support. Please contact us if you need any assistance.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258537129184"
    },
    "gp_section_572024258537194720": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f0c7adc0428ac90c0b451f3c203493c412bd9446381fa1e2f807e3813b2d4413_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>It’s why stretching only helps for a few minutes. Why painkillers wear off. And why the discomfort keeps coming back. <strong>Until the root cause is stabilized, the cycle continues.</strong></p>",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>Get back to moving freely without pain, pills, or constant appointments holding you back.</strong></span>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>But when you support the body where it needs it most, everything starts to shift. Literally.</p>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Your Pain Isn’t Random - It’s Structural.",
        "ggX187CCedu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-bea03ca1-3789-4668-8a1b-75fca5cf575d.webp",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Most lower back, hip, and sciatic pain comes from <strong>instability in the spine and pelvis</strong>, specifically the sacroiliac joint. When this area falls out of alignment, it puts pressure on surrounding nerves, disrupts your natural movement, and leads to chronic tension and inflammation.</p>",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Your Pain Isn’t Random - It’s Structural."
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258537194720"
    },
