        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>“I Thought It Would Be Uncomfortable But It’s Not”</p>",
        "gg9YwQ98cbE_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4a6ecdcc-9107-4943-850c-c62257b49429.webp",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>“Everything Else I Tried Just Made It Worse”</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>I’ve wasted money on braces, gadgets, massage guns, you name it. Most of them either made the pain worse or were too uncomfortable to actually use. The SmoothSpine belt was different. It felt solid but comfortable, and I noticed a difference the same day I started wearing it. After two weeks, I was sleeping better and walking without limping. This is the only thing that’s actually worked.</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>- Laura K., 38</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>- Amanda W., 36</p>",
        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p>I have a desk job and was worried this would be bulky or awkward to wear at work. But it’s slim, easy to adjust, and I forget I even have it on. Before this belt, I’d get this awful hip pain after sitting too long. Now I wear the belt a few hours a day and haven’t felt that pain in weeks. It’s subtle but seriously effective.</p>",
        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>- Emily R., 41</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>I honestly didn’t think a belt could do anything for my back pain. I’ve had sciatica flare-ups for years, and nothing ever helped for more than a day or two. But I gave this belt a shot out of desperation and within a week, I was walking without that stabbing nerve pain down my leg. I wear it a couple hours a day and feel like myself again.</p>",
        "ggoEhqLoXFB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-94a48c29-eead-4dac-8ec6-c0d7fb2bb11d.webp",
        "ggrydDXALPH_text": "Real Users, Real Life-Changing Results"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572024258537391328"
    },
